04:04.679 --> 04:07.508
-OOH, IT'S MALIBU
MANUEL TO THE RESCUE.

04:08.204 --> 04:10.337
OH, I'M SORRY, ESE,
THEY'RE CALLING YOU MANNY

04:10.467 --> 04:11.381
NOW, HUH, DOG?

04:12.121 --> 04:13.514
PRETTY SOON YOU'LL
BE CHANGING YOUR NAME

04:13.644 --> 04:15.080
TO MICHAEL AND HOOKING
UP WITH SOME BLONDE

04:15.211 --> 04:16.865
CHICA FROM MALIBU WHO
DON'T EVEN KNOW THAT

04:16.995 --> 04:18.606
YOU USED TO BE
ONE OF US, ESE.

04:18.736 --> 04:21.261
-KNOW WHAT, I HAVEN'T
CHANGED ANYTHING ABOUT ME.

04:22.218 --> 04:23.567
-FORGET THIS FOOL, MAN.

04:23.698 --> 04:25.308
