04:35.579 --> 04:36.972
GIVE A BROTHER A
LITTLE RED UNIFORM AND

04:37.102 --> 04:38.321
HE DON'T REMEMBER NOTHING.

04:39.235 --> 04:41.672
HOMEBOYS LIKE ME CAN'T
AFFORD SWIMSUITS, ESE,

04:41.803 --> 04:43.718
WE GOTTA MAKE DUE
WITH WHAT WE GOT.

04:43.848 --> 04:45.589
OR DON'T YOU
REMEMBER THAT?

04:48.200 --> 04:50.551
-[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

05:16.011 --> 05:20.581
