-GRAB HIM!

06:12.633 --> 06:13.547
COME ON!

06:13.677 --> 06:14.939
-I GOT HIM.

06:18.682 --> 06:20.554
-[INAUDIBLE]

06:20.684 --> 06:22.120
-I DON'T THINK
HE'S BREATHING!

06:22.251 --> 06:23.557
-CHECK HIS AIRWAY!

06:24.558 --> 06:26.037
-NOTHING!

06:26.168 --> 06:27.169
-[SIRENS WAILING]
-MANNY: THERE'S NO PULSE!

06:27.299 --> 06:28.388
WE'RE LOSING HIM!

06:29.214 --> 06:30.955
-APRIL: START CPR!

06:31.086 --> 06:34.263
-ONE, TWO,
THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

06:34.394 --> 06:35.656
-[BREATH]

06:35.786 --> 06:38.572
-ONE, TWO,
THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

06:38.702 --> 06:40.574
-[BREATH]

