-ALL RIGHT, BAG HIM.

06:53.108 --> 06:54.979
-ONE, TWO,
THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

06:55.110 --> 06:56.241
-HOW LONG WAS HE DOWN?

06:56.372 --> 06:57.591
-HE GOT CAUGHT
IN A RIPTIDE,

06:57.721 --> 06:59.157
WE BARELY GOT
TO HIM IN TIME.

06:59.288 --> 07:00.768
-IF WE GOT HIM IN TIME.

07:00.898 --> 07:04.728
ONE, TWO,
THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

07:04.859 --> 07:08.602
ONE, TWO,
THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

